Enum APIConstants.BillNames

    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<APIConstants.BillNames>

    APIConstants

    public static enum APIConstants.BillNames
extends java.lang.Enum<APIConstants.BillNames>
    Enumerated bill enables for a bill validator ICommDevice.
    Pyramid designates up to twelve(12) slots for notes.
    RS-232 supports ONLY 7 notes.
    Since:
    1.0.0.0
    Author:
    Cory Todd
